       <title>Gold Price Hits Year High</title>
       <chapter>                                                   <!--[0-N]-->
        <paragraph>After 12 months of continuous growth, on March 4th, 2016, gold price hit an historical peak.
             The highest price was 1,920 USD/oz.</paragraph>                        <!--[0-N]-->
        <paragraph>There was a growth of 17% because the investors
           are trying to grab gold as a safe haven because of great uncertainty in global monetary policy.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Oil prices are falling of 0.65%, so investors have decided to move their investments on gold.</paragraph>
